  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This study examines how the PEERS (Laugeson &amp; Frankel, 2010; Laugeson, 2016)
      social-behavioral intervention affects social relationships, and brain development and
      function in adolescents and young adults with autism spectrum disorder.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
